---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Blog
description: Shorter writing on AI developments, ideas and what they mean.
permalink: /blog/
---
<section class="section">
  <div class="wrap">
    <header class="list-header">
      <p class="eyebrow mono">NOTES & ANALYSIS</p>
      <h1>Blog</h1>
      <p class="dek">Shorter, more frequent writing — recent developments in AI and what I make of them.</p>
    </header>
    <ul class="post-list">
      {% for post in collections.posts %}
      <li class="post-row" data-reveal>
        <a href="{{ post.url }}">
          <span class="post-row-date mono">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</span>
          <span class="post-row-body">
            <span class="post-row-title">{{ post.data.title }}</span>
            {% if post.data.description %}<span class="post-row-dek">{{ post.data.description }}</span>{% endif %}
          </span>
        </a>
      </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>
